{"title":"红旗歌","authors":["李季"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":6,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李季"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要打鼓不敲锣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听我唱个红旗歌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗就是总路线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高举红旗幸福多。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总路线是灯塔满天红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照得社会主义大道亮又明。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总路线是进军号，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"号声震得山摇地皮动。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总路线是红旗呼啦啦飘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把人心都照亮了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人高举大红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看谁举得比天高。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举起红旗要勇敢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敢想敢说又敢干。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天不怕来地不怕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻天复地要数咱！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗就是跃进旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高举红旗撵太阳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粮食要堆成昆仑山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炼炉里要炼出万万吨钢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家都来插红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"插满了平川插高山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"城市乡村都插遍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗插到心里边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗就是胜利旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"插到哪里哪里就胜利。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"资本主义的白旗连根拔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扯下白旗换红旗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各色杂旗都扯掉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"单要红旗照大地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗就是幸福旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗就是幸福的社会主义。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}